Required documents for admission

When applying for admission to Dalian Jiaotong University (Railway Institute) in China you should prepare all required documents. Request a list of necessary documents directly from a university, as it may vary for different countries. Using our live chat, you can also ask for sample documents.

Student visa

Research proposal outline (MA, PhD)

Passport

Declaration for financial support

TOEFL Certificate

Photographs

Proof of fee payment

Health and Life Insurance

Online Application form
